<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About OnTrack</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html, body {
      height: auto !important;
      min-height: 100% !important;
      overflow-y: auto !important;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      overflow-y: auto;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    .contact-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .contact-title .highlight {
      color: #ffd700;
    }

    .steps {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 350;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }

    .emphasis {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 350;
      margin: 0.5rem;
      color: #ffd700;
    }


    .form-group-wrapper {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .form-control {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      border: 1px solid #333333;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .form-control::placeholder {
      color: #808080;
    }

    .form-control:focus {
      background-color: #222222;
      border-color: #ffd700;
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .btn-send {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-send:hover {
      background-color: #ffd700;
      border-color: #ffd700;
      color: #000000;
    }

    .contact-box {
      padding: 1rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }


    .contact-info p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      color: #cccccc;
    }

    .contact-info .highlight {
      color: #ffd700;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-box">
      <h1 class="contact-title">
        How to use <span class="highlight">OnTrack</span>?
      </h1>
      <p class="lead px-4">
        <p class="emphasis">OnTrack is super simple.</p>
        <p class="emphasis">No need to login, spend hours inputting your courses, or to decipher complicated charts.</p>
        <p class="emphasis">Just upload your transcript, and we'll do the rest!</p>
      </p>
      <br></br>

      <ol class="steps px-4">
        <li>Enter your Major and Term. This helps us understand your academic context and tailor the requirements accordingly.</li>
        <br></br>
        <li>Upload your transcript. Our system will analyze your courses and show you exactly where you stand in terms of degree requirements. If you would rather input your courses manually, we have that option too!</li>
        <br></br>
        <li>Review your progress. OnTrack will provide a clear breakdown of which requirements you've completed, which ones are in progress, and which ones you still need to fulfill. if you find something that doesn't look right, you can always edit your courses and requirements to make sure everything is accurate.</li>
        <br></br>
      </ol>

        <h2 class="lead px-4 fw-bold">
            It's that easy! OnTrack is designed to be user-friendly and intuitive, so you can focus on your studies while we help you stay on track for graduation.
        </h2>



    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>